      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥绫菜",
      "voice": {
        "id": "AYAN_002_AYAN011B_040",
        "file": "voice/ayan_002_ayan011B_040.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「哈，哈啊！肛门性交太棒了！",
        "哦哦，哦哦！嗯嗯嗯，哦呼呼！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV046・アヘ顔・エロ下着",
        "file": "EV046_05"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "深入抽插，轻轻擦拭，彻底刺激绫姐的肛门。",
        "",
        "姐姐的身体完全接受了它，将其作为快感接受了进来。",
        ""
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV046・アヘ顔・エロ下着",
        "file": "EV046_05"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥绫菜",
      "voice": {
        "id": "AYAN_002_AYAN011B_041",
        "file": "voice/ayan_002_ayan011B_041.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「哈啊，哈啊！这么厉害的事情，教，教我，真开心啊，嗯哦哦！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV046・アヘ顔・エロ下着",
        "file": "EV046_05"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "",
        "如果你这么说，我也很高兴。",
        "不仅得到了绫姐的第一次，而且还能感受到快感。",
        ""
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV046・アヘ顔・エロ下着",
        "file": "EV046_05"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_AYAN_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_ayan_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥绫菜",
      "voice": {
        "id": "AYAN_002_AYAN011B_042",
        "file": "voice/ayan_002_ayan011B_042.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「嗯嗯，嗯呼！再多一点！",
        "再深入肛门！」"
